ManualRejectReconciliation is an ActionForm
    action is ManualRejectReconciliation
    Layout
        header3 of "EnterYourReasonForRejectingBankStatement<BankStatement>Reconciliation"
        visible when (RejectStatementReconReasonCodeRequired)
            paragraph
                reason code
                reason code.Description
                    no label
                    display as text
        single column
            PrmComment
                label is "Comment"
                use text area of 10 lines
